dct_description_sm: Iraq. Mudiriyat al-Misaha al-Ammah. Iraq. Directorate General of Surveys. [[Map of Iraq]: Afak section.] Alternate title: Liwa' ad-Diwaniyah: qada' 'Afak: nahiyat 'Afak. [ad-Diwaniyah province: Afak district; Afak section.] Relief shown by hachures, form lines, and contour lines at .5 meter intervals. Triangulation points are shown. Surveyed: 1931.Tribal lands and ownership are shown.
